From: KOSHIKAWA Kenichi <reishoku.misc@pm.me>
Date: 2026-01-28
Subject: rpmdev-spectool: accept -v as version alias

help2man invokes rpmdev-spectool with -v. Accept it as a version alias.

---
 rpmdev-spectool | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

--- a/rpmdev-spectool
+++ b/rpmdev-spectool
@@ -88,6 +88,7 @@
     ops.add_argument(
         "--version",
         "-V",
+        "-v",
         action="version",
         version="%(prog)s {}".format(__version__),
         help="Print the version and exit",
